Hi Brendan, 
Thanks again for discussing scheduling with me last week. As an update, the Court has issued a scheduling order for the 
trial (attached). Jury selection will occur during the week of November 15th, and the trial will begin on November 29th. 
Thanks, 
From: Quigley, Brendan 
Sent: Monday, May 10, 2021 8:50 AM

Subject: Rodgers 
C 
Thanks for your call last week. Neither Mr. Rodgers nor I currently have any un-movable commitments between 
September and December. As I mentioned, I'm waiting for trial dates for 1-2 trials as courts open back up, so please let 
me know when the Maxwell trial gets scheduled.
